title: File:Secretary of Defense Lloyd Austin participates in a wreath laying ceremony at the Monument of the Unknown Soldier in Luanda, Angola on September 27, 2023 - 230927-D-PM193-1736.jpg
author: U.S. Secretary of Defense
description: Secretary of Defense Lloyd J. Austin III participates in a wreath laying ceremony at the Monument of the Unknown Soldier in Luanda, Angola, Sept. 27, 2023. Austin met with Djiboutian officials to discuss ongoing military cooperation, regional security challenges, and opportunities for further collaboration. (DoD photo by U.S. Navy Petty Officer 1st Class Alexander Kubitza)
